  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the long term results of laparoscopic
      sacrocolpopexy regarding anatomical results, recurrences, complications, further surgeries
      required, patients satisfaction and quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
